            <thetext>As I talked just to Thomas, he told me that the dependency logging mechanism on generator side does not care about the #require, #optional and #use statements in the code. It does only reflect the dependencies the code itself has. For further optimizations, it is necessary to know what the outcome would be and not what the code would look like in the end.</thetext>
